{
  "chapter": 32,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙一行在关朴军马护送下渡过黄河抵达魏都大梁。信陵君魏无忌隆重迎接，但魏王下令除项少龙和赵倩女眷外余人须在城外扎营。信陵君在书斋接见项少龙，分析天下大势，指出秦国二十年内难复元气，并透露灰胡实为龙阳君亲信，龙阳君对项少龙恨之入骨。信陵君暗示先发制人刺杀魏王的计划，项少龙识破平原夫人母子的连环毒计，被迫虚与委蛇表忠投诚。信陵君又提及赵穆必不容项少龙回赵，使其进退两难。项少龙向赵雅坦白处境，赵雅展现情报能力，指出禁止成胥入城乃信陵君之计，并拿出信陵君府鸟瞰图。项少龙决定夜探信陵君住处寻找《鲁公秘录》，赵雅提供避犬药粉相助。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你确是不凡，能以区区数百之众，力抗过万马贼，难怪你在赵国冒起得如此之快。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "全赖君上果断英明，领军有方，才能使秦人遭逢自商鞅变法以来最惨痛的败绩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "秦昭王心胸狭窄，有白起如此名将，竟为一时意气，硬把他逼死，范雎又于四年前罢相，使秦势大弱，旋被我国攻陷陶郡，若我猜估不错，秦人在二十年内休想恢复元气。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "难怪君上如此得天下人望，确是见解精辟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！若要使三晋合一，此其时也。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "家姊的确没有看错你，项少龙果然是有胆有识之人。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙知否正身陷进退两难的险境？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你还是不知道！告诉我，你知否灰胡是谁人的亲信？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "灰胡不是听命于贵王吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "安厘是个胆怯的家伙，怎敢沾手这种触犯众怒的事。这些暗里为非作歹的事，全是由安厘最宠爱的龙阳君一手包办。据密报龙阳君现在对你恨之入骨，所以才逼安厘下令不许贵属入城，好使你孤立无援，若非得我强护着你，少龙早死无葬身之地。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "龙阳君名列魏国三大剑手榜上，人又精明狡诈，绝不容易应付。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "我这可算是进不得，但为何退也不能呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "因为你若就此回赵，赵穆必然会置你于死地。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "实不相瞒，今天我奉命来魏，实怀有密令，要盗取《鲁公秘录》。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好！现在我才相信你有投诚之意，假设你能为我好好办事，本君保证你荣华富贵，终身享之不尽。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "安厘这家伙在龙阳君怂恿下，现正密锣紧鼓准备灭赵，所以即使灰胡和他全无关系，也绝不肯放你这种人才回去。至于赵倩不但做不成储妃，命运还会非常凄惨。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "现在应怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先发制人，后发制于人，这道理少龙明白吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "若有用得着我项少龙的地方，君上尽管吩咐，赴汤蹈火，在所不辞。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有你这几句话，何愁大事不成。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我心中早有定计，不过仍未到告诉你的时候，这几天你可尽情享乐，我府内美女如云，你爱哪个伺候都可以。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "text": "我有雅夫人便心满意足。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你真懂得选择，赵雅狐媚过人，确是男人私房内的恩物，你尽情享受吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_ling_jun",
      "speaker_name": "信陵君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今晚你先好好休息，明天让我给你安排点节目，包保你不虚此行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项郎你受到什么打击，为何脸色如此难看？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "假若《鲁公秘录》现已落入我的手里，我会立刻带你们偷出大梁，远走高飞。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙啊！振作点好吗？看见你这样子，人家心都痛了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不准成胥等人进城，完全与安厘王无关。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你怎会知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "所以不要以为我们全无反抗之力，我们赵国在各处均广布眼线，信陵君府内亦有我的人。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此事必与信陵君有关，故意使你觉得孤立无援，生出危机重重的感觉，于是惟有任他们姊弟摆布你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你查到《鲁公秘录》的藏处没有？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "假设你明知有人来盗取你的东西，你会随便让人知道吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "哪里弄来这么好的东西？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "别忘记人家是干哪一行的，若连这样的宝贝都弄不到，怎么偷更重要的东西呢？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "若真有《鲁公秘录》，信陵君怎不拿去依图制造，还留在府内干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这牵涉到信陵君和魏王的斗争，信陵君一天未坐上王位，一天不会把《秘录》拿出来，所以《秘录》必藏在府内某隐秘处。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "恐怕我未找到《秘录》，早给信陵君这奸鬼害死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要说不吉利的话好吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你有没有方法联络上乌卓等人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这么简单的事，尽管交给我办！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你要乌卓设法在营地打条通往别处的地道，有起事来，说不定能救命呢！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "情势不是那么严重吧？我们终是赵王的代表……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你若知道魏王有攻打赵国之心，就不会这样说了，今天我们是来错了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不陪人家吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "信陵君随时会逼我去行刺魏王，时间无多，我定要尽快查出《鲁公秘录》的藏处。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "魏无忌的住处有恶犬守卫，闯入定会给他发觉。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你是偷东西的专家，自然有应付恶犬的方法。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只要撒点这些药粉在身上，恶犬都会避开你。可是那里不但有恶犬，还有守卫，唉！既知道你这样去冒险，人家今晚怎还睡得着？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你脱光衣服在床上放心等我吧！保证没有人可看到我的影子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    }
  ],
